Identify and measure mobilization factors
On the contrary, the managerial revolution necessary for the proper functioning of modern enterprises, presupposes a finalist vision of human behaviour.
It consists of integrating, in any reasoning or practice of governance, a fundamental finding: for employees, commitment to the enterprise is only possible if it appears clearly as a means of achieving part of their dreams, ambitions and projects.
